Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I WANT TO CHANGE THE WORLD　源源不绝的热情{\fad(500,00)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:12.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着怦然心动的未来  伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:18.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能够放出光芒　IT'S WONDERLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:24.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来那无法预测的黑夜  震撼着你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:31.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法相信任何东西  你充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:39.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你相遇的瞬间  我找到了真正的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:48.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自觉的温柔呈现在面前  把我们唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:55.31,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I WANT TO CHANGE THE WORLD　不会再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:01:05.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要构筑起跟你在一起的未来  就能飞向任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:10.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHANGE MY MIND　源源不绝的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:15.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着未知的明天  张开双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能够展翅飞翔　IT'S WONDERLAND{\fad(0000,480)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:17.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 在生命的旅程中{\fad(400,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:23.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地 失去所有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:29.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:36.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:46.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在那深深的丛林中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定埋藏着 被丢弃的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:58.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能把握时光的轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:05.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许 能再次飞翔{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:13.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:19.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存下去 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:25.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:32.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1000)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能杀了他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 奈落大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉 弥勒 还有珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 奈落大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被窃取的铁碎牙 决战 奈落之城！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我让他忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把犬夜叉的刀铁碎牙抢来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就让琥珀永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…刚刚睡醒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会杀了他…虽然觉得很对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 那个人根本不是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是琥珀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我弟弟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能做出杀死村民的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要…把他跟奈落一起除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么简单吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的容貌没有任何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能轻易的憎恨他 忘了他的一切吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能落入这种卑劣的圈套里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换做是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能也下不了手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为容貌丝毫没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是无法憎恨或遗忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉说的是桔梗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意 我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 弥勒！你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的风穴还没完全康复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别为了那些杂碎去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只要由我来干掉头目就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂碎给我滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的力量也想跟我交手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！可恶可恶 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太心软了 实在太心软了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奈落的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非杀了这小子不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种人 死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 伙伴 还有村人们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 像我这种人…死了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你干什么？你想怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子想把四魂碎片取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才弄伤自己的背部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维系着琥珀性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是埋在他体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把它取出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀立刻就会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在试探我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看我能不能亲手送上铁碎牙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的本意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？犬夜叉 还有弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没消失 那小鬼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀的血腥味还残留着 一直闻的到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落在引诱我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴被封印 铁碎牙又被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他的 我还有这双拳头！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先将飞来骨放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遵照约定把犬夜叉的刀 铁碎牙带来了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我才会把刀给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落 现在马上把琥珀变回原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使把我杀了也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能不清楚这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是四魂之玉造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要四魂碎片的妖怪 袭击了你的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的死 琥珀徘徊在生与死之间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是四魂之玉的因果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀害了父亲与伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为你想要四魂之玉的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就被你杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:10:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人因四魂之力而生 亦因四魂之力而死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要厌恶四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀就是依靠它的力量生存着的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照约定 是用刀换琥珀吧 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙无耻 什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的答案 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城的少主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荫刀是个宅心仁厚的主君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他慎重地埋葬了除妖师的骸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派人去保护你的 也是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了他吗 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人见荫刀…现在我就是城主 荫刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比我的瘴气更毒的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 愿意跟琥珀一起在这城中侍奉我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荫刀也说过呢 叫你回到城中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我胡说八道 除掉你才是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了父亲和伙伴的仇恨 我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到城了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是奈落的城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是珊瑚的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀 快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那双手杀了弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后只需渴望 渴望自己能生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想让自己得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了琥珀 染上鲜血之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片就能增加黑暗之光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之光正因为其污浊 才更美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能下得了手杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…下不了手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被弟弟所伤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了…为何做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落…你在哪 滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害父亲与同伴的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐却无法取其性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟比她自己的生命更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何能达到如此境界 我实在想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点 只差一点就能恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉 这不是跟你当年的情况一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟50年前的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让珊瑚憎恨弟弟 让她亲手杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此 他背上的四魂碎片就会沾染邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和让彼此信赖的桔梗与犬夜叉互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自相残杀的圈套一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 我绝对无法饶恕这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像桔梗为了不让四魂之玉被污染而死去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚也…没有与弟弟交战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那家伙真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚怎么可能会做出那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为珊瑚…是个爱护弟弟的好姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是瘴气！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肤浅的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淹没在瘴气之海中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过父亲说了哦 琥珀的功夫越来越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次被父亲夸奖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 你还不能乱动…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 你别乱动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会我还有一大堆怨言跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！奈落…那家伙拥有四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落！觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落…你真是太差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人…这种力量是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将邪念 瘴气和毒气都一扫而空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种力量是桔梗的…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你求饶我也不会原谅你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确就是桔梗的破魔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这丫头是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 它穿透瘴气把奈落射穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不能放开云母哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那是城的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落逃走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…因为四魂碎片消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没能干掉奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用自责 若没有戈薇小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家早就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇 好像刚才的你是目前为止最强的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉…绝对要打倒奈落哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多么艰难 大家都要同心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 珊瑚 不能乱动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点阻止她 珊瑚好像想走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 你想去什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我已无法跟大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 大家都知道你是因为弟弟才被奈落欺骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要琥珀还在奈落手里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚 你打算一个人去讨伐奈落吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…让大家一起去救你的弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落不是你一个人能对付的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 首先得包扎伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唧唧歪歪的吵死了 大家在一起就是比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也蛮会打架的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连轻易被夺走铁碎牙的犬夜叉都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？应该没有问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说的好像是我很呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你心胸宽大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚讨厌我们大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的缘故 使大家遭受这种危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往后可能还会重蹈覆辙…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…一直都很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有大家陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为咬了奈落 而被瘴气侵蚀的云母
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有一种草药能够治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和犬夜叉前往药草田的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰见了身躯庞大 在田里工作的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然力大无穷  看起来很吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个妖怪 有着一双温柔的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地善良但哀愁的地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.78,0:24:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:25:00.00,KEYPOINT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与珊瑚很亲密的猫又 平时是只小猫{\pos(331,288)}
